title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/compareNode\"><code>compareNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/comparePoint\"><code>comparePoint()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/createContextualFragment\"><code>createContextualFragment()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/deleteContents\"><code>deleteContents()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/detach\"><code>detach()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/extractContents\"><code>extractContents()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/getBoundingClientRect\"><code>getBoundingClientRect()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/getClientRects\"><code>getClientRects()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/insertNode\"><code>insertNode()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/intersectsNode\"><code>intersectsNode()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/isPointInRange\"><code>isPointInRange()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/selectNode\"><code>selectNode()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/selectNodeContents\"><code>selectNodeContents()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/setEnd\"><code>setEnd()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setEndAfter\"><code>setEndAfter()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setEndBefore\"><code>setEndBefore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/setStart\"><code>setStart()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setStartAfter\"><code>setStartAfter()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/setStartBefore\"><code>setStartBefore()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/surroundContents\"><code>surroundContents()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/toString\"><code>toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code><strong>Range.startOffset</strong></code>&nbsp;是一个只读属性，用于返回一个表示&nbsp;<code style=\"font-style: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">Range</code>&nbsp;在&nbsp;<code style=\"font-style: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">startContainer</code>&nbsp;中的起始位置的数字。</p>\n\n<p>如果&nbsp;<code>startContainer</code> 是一个文本（<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code></a>）、注释（<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code></a>）或者 CDATA 区块（<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CDATASection\"><code>CDATASection</code></a>）节点，那么返回的偏移量是从&nbsp;<code style=\"font-style: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">startContainer</code>&nbsp;开始到&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a> 的边界点的字符数量。对于其他的节点类型，&nbsp;<code style=\"font-style: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">startOffset</code>&nbsp;返回&nbsp;<code style=\"font-style: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">startContainer</code>&nbsp;到边界点的子节点数量。</p>\n\n<p>可使用<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/setStart\"><code>Range.setStart</code></a> 方法改变&nbsp;<code style=\"font-style: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">Range</code>&nbsp;的&nbsp;<code style=\"font-style: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">startOffset</code>&nbsp;位置。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>startRangeOffset</em> = <em>range</em>.startOffset;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>range <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createRange</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nrange<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setStart</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>startNode<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>startOffset<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nrange<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setEnd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>endNode<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>endOffset<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nstartRangeOffset <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> range<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>startOffset<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"specification","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#ref-for-dom-range-startoffset①","title":"DOM Standard"}],"query":"api.Range.startOffset"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Range.startOffset","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/startOffset/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"compat-mobile\"></div>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model\" title=\"/en-US/docs/DOM/DOM_Reference\">The DOM interfaces index</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"syntax"},{"text":"示例","id":"example"},{"text":"规范","id":"specification"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"Range.startOffset 是一个只读属性，用于返回一个表示 Range 在 startContainer 中的起始位置的数字。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Range.startOffset","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Range.startOffset","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/range/startoffset","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/range/startoffset/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range","title":"Range"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range/startOffset","title":"Range.startOffset"